heading_context: Prove you qualify for Child Benefit
chunks.html_content: Child Benefit award notices have replaced Child Benefit numbers as the main way to prove your eligibility. You will not have a Child Benefit number if you first claimed after 23 February 2021.

heading_context: Prove you qualify for Child Benefit
If you need other proof you qualify
If you use the online service
chunks.html_content:
You may be able to:

  • use a bank statement showing Child Benefit going into your account
  • use the online service or the HMRC app to print your proof of entitlement page or save it as a document to use as proof

To use this service, youll need to prove your identity using Government Gateway. Youll be able to register for Government Gateway if you have not used it before.
